{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5655d212a2","title":"诬蔑党的领导人（二）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"42cd967584","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"5655d212a2"}],"tags":[{"id":"5fd56865b0","name":"彭真","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"018b7bda33","name":"李德"},{"id":"3dd9465822","name":"贾梅"},{"id":"55d4e5b786","name":"中国人民大学"},{"id":"791151edc4","name":"杨森达赖"},{"id":"adca402036","name":"李向春"},{"id":"b031e33f83","name":"王鸿章"},{"id":"f58879f35d","name":"杜树芸"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4c407f80be","type":"title","text":"诬蔑党的领导人（二）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"09264bdbf9","type":"authors","text":"中国人民大学杜树芸李德王鸿章杨森达赖李向春贾梅","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"b039246d84","type":"paragraph","text":"“中共中央领导同志工农出身的不多，都是知识分子，因此是知识分子领导，不是工人阶级领导。”（中国人民大学马列主义研究班研究生  杜树芸）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"f945e7ea6b","type":"paragraph","text":"“最近和同学们辩论“民主”这个题目，我感到吃亏：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"e8c5cda85d","type":"paragraph","text":"第一、和他们辩论损失了我的人格。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"759a923b91","type":"paragraph","text":"第二、他们用彭真来吓唬人，其实彭真不还是人类历史上不足道也的小卒，可能会犯荒谬绝伦的错误。他们仿佛找到了靠山，这只能说明他们在事实面前是何等无能，对真理是何等胆怯（原为“却”字——编者）！”（中国人民大学哲学系学生  李德）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"ee1be9fee2","type":"paragraph","text":"“贺龙靠一把菜刀起家，根本不懂外文，也随总理出国。”（中国人民大学计划系学生  王鸿章）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"6aee970ad7","type":"paragraph","text":"“周扬为中央的宣传副部长……没拿出象样的作品，只是接接外宾，作开幕闭幕词等等，只是靠党员吃饭。”（中国人民大学历史系学生  杨森达赖）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"67c0c4e962","type":"paragraph","text":"“同志们：让我们再来回望一下那些高贵的首长，那些高贵的领导吧！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"b46a8d8e86","type":"paragraph","text":"他们吃得饱了，肩膀也宽了，他们的身体显得特别笨重。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"2bb2ef5a16","type":"paragraph","text":"因为官僚主义已经形成，他们出门必须乘坐汽车！","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"f1abf0185b","type":"paragraph","text":"连同他的孩子和老婆，有限的办公时间签字吸烟！","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"aa5ffd7fb5","type":"paragraph","text":"看来这也非常麻烦讨厌！不问德才如何专看是否党员！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"3266ea4de0","type":"paragraph","text":"我想这种制度只有在西医才能看见！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"0f9cd75181","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党同志！领导同志！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"7c489ad41f","type":"paragraph","text":"你们生活和农民生活差得太远了。你们住着楼房还想着疗养院！可是你们是否知道还有农民草房漏着天，你们已经渐渐地渐渐地腐化了！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"2517326ae8","type":"paragraph","text":"你们已经渐渐地渐渐地把农民忘了！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"6767a25c39","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党同志你怎么了？我还记得你们穿着补绽衣服。”（中国人民大学历史系学生 李向春）","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"03c10f6392","type":"paragraph","text":"“中央应当公开承认在党国事务中的错误和缺点，不要总把责任推在下级干部身上。”（中国人民大学工业经济系学生  贾梅）","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"},{"id":"7ae0b1eb01","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2"}],"page":{"id":"2f9b35f345","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5655d212a2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}